[*] Frequently asked questions:

 Q. Where can I get help for DC++?
 A. It's available in your programs help menu and here: https://web.archive.org/web/20240330030439/https://www.dslreports.com/faq/dc/
	DC++ answers are available here: https://answers.launchpad.net/dcplusplus/

 Q. Where can I get updates to my DC++ client?
 A. Updates can be downloaded here: https://dcplusplus.sourceforge.io/

 Q. Is there an alternative to DC++?
 A. Yes, very good and modern client is AirDC++: https://airdcpp.net/

 Q. Why I don't get any search results and can't download from other users?
 A. This has something to do with settings in your client.
	Follow this link: https://web.archive.org/web/20240330030439/https://www.dslreports.com/faq/6524/

 Q. Where can I get more information about Verlihub?
 A. Verlihub website is here: https://github.com/verlihub/
	Support hub is here: nmdcs://hub.verlihub.net:7777

 Anything not covered above should be asked in main chat.
